data.description: Welcome to 492 Old 30 Rd, a spacious haven just outside the city limits. This inviting home boasts 4 bedrooms with a bonus room, and 3 full bathrooms, providing ample space for your family's needs.The heart of the home is a well-designed kitchen, perfect for preparing meals and creating memories. The open living area offers a cozy atmosphere, ideal for relaxation and entertaining.With a 2-car garage, you'll have plenty of space for vehicles and storage. This property offers the tranquility of rural living while maintaining convenient access to city amenities.Currently operating as an Airbnb, this home presents a unique income opportunity. Additionally, the furniture is negotiable, allowing you to move in with ease or continue with its successful Airbnb operation. Don't miss the opportunity to make 492 Old 30 Rd your new home. Explore the spaciousness and charm this property offers. Schedule a viewing today!
